CLAUDE.md
# Ship only the built bundles from dist/, never their source maps. vsce force-includes any
# file matched by a negation, so we un-ignore the bundles by extension — NOT `!dist/**`,
# which would drag dist/*.map back in past the `**/*.map` rule above.
!dist/*.cjs
!dist/*.mjs
!media/**
!walkthroughs/**
